{
  "stem": "18626.13",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, that's the best rollers I had in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, she's so impressed with the rollers I turned out for the lawn mower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let me find a place does have lawn mowers and shops who fix the lawn mowers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll go to them and I'll tell them I make rollers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they gave me all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I brought a sample.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they all gave me-- make me five.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Make me three.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Make me eight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Make me 10.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then I start to figure out, that piece of wood alone cost $0.20.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it's only left $0.30 to turn a roller.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's not enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What I do?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "To raise them?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I cannot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They get them from New York, even my rollers are better, nicer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So one day, it came to my mind, I remembered that my uncle in New York told me a story that in the wartime, what it make him-- what it made him stand on his feet to make a dollar is he made balls for the army.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's called Skee balls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The soldiers on the ships played Skee balls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They roll a ball and it goes in in a-- in numbers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And what did he use for the balls to make?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The old bowling pins from the bowling alleys, what they got to throw out, the little cheap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the bowling pins got to be in good shape when you play bowling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he went to the old bowling alleys in New York and he got them for nothing, because otherwise, they were going to throw it out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he made the bowling-- the balls for the Skee balls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So it came to my mind in Miami, let me go and find where the bowling alleys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I went on 36th Street.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
